<h2>What's New</h2>

<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Fix repeating credential file dialog appearing on every auto-refresh cycle when credentials are missing</li>
</ul>

Previously, when Claude Code credentials were not found, the file picker dialog would appear repeatedly during every auto-refresh cycle (every 5 minutes by default). This release fixes the issue by properly handling the missing credentials case without triggering the dialog.

---

See <a href="https://github.com/tartinerlabs/ClaudeMeter/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md">CHANGELOG.md</a> for full release history.
